my (<a href=\"https://lemmy.fediverse.observer/list\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">List</a>)</li>\n<li>Jira / Asana / Trello -> <a href=\"https://community.taiga.io/t/taiga-30min-setup/170\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Taiga</a> or <a href=\"https://tenzu.net/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Tenzu</a></li>\n<li>Asana</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"other-free-tools\" style=\"position:relative;\">Other free tools<a href=\"#other-free-tools\" aria-label=\"other free tools permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>Something less known as GIMP or blender and not specifically a Google's counterpart but some remarkable free software that frees you from online services.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/keeweb/keeweb\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">KeeWeb</a> is a browser and desktop password manager</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/donetick/donetick\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Donetick</a> - todolist</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"other-steps\" style=\"position:relative;\">Other steps<a href=\"#other-steps\" aria-label=\"other steps permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1